graph TB
    subgraph ModelRegistry["Model Registry Component"]
        direction TB

        subgraph CoreServices["Core Services"]
            Proxy["model-registry proxy<br/>Go REST Service<br/>:8080/TCP"]
            Catalog["model-catalog server<br/>Go REST Service<br/>:8080/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph Satellites["Satellite Components"]
            Controller["model-registry controller<br/>Go K8s Controller<br/>:8081/TCP (health)"]
            CSI["CSI storage initializer<br/>Go Init Container"]
            AsyncJob["async-upload job<br/>Python K8s Job"]
        end

        subgraph UI["UI Layer"]
            BFF["UI BFF<br/>Go HTTP Server<br/>:8080/TCP"]
            Frontend["React SPA<br/>TypeScript"]
            Frontend -->|served by| BFF
        end

        subgraph Data["Data Layer"]
            EmbedMD["EmbedMD<br/>(Embedded Metadata Store)<br/>GORM ORM"]
        end

        Proxy --> EmbedMD
        Catalog --> CatalogDB["Catalog PostgreSQL"]
    end

    %% External Users
    User["Data Scientist / Client"] -->|REST API| Proxy
    User -->|Browse UI| BFF
    Dashboard["OpenShift AI Dashboard"] -->|REST API| Proxy

    %% Controller interactions
    Controller -->|syncs metadata| Proxy
    Controller -->|watches| InferenceServiceCR["InferenceService CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io)"]
    Controller -->|updates| InferenceServiceCR

    %% CSI interactions
    KServeAgent["KServe Agent"] -->|init container| CSI
    CSI -->|resolves model-registry:// URI| Proxy
    CSI -->|downloads model| StorageBackend["Storage Backend<br/>(S3/GCS)"]

    %% Async job interactions
    AsyncJob -->|registers model| Proxy
    AsyncJob -->|download/upload| S3["S3 Storage"]
    AsyncJob -->|push/pull images| OCI["OCI Registry"]
    AsyncJob -->|download models| HF_Job["HuggingFace"]
    AsyncJob -.->|sign artifacts| Sigstore["Sigstore<br/>(Fulcio/Rekor)"]

    %% Catalog interactions
    Catalog -->|fetches metadata| HF["HuggingFace API"]

    %% BFF interactions
    BFF -->|forwards API calls| Proxy
    BFF -->|forwards catalog calls| Catalog

    %% Data layer
    EmbedMD -->|SQL| PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL 16+"]
    EmbedMD -->|SQL| MySQL["MySQL 8.3+"]

    %% Service Mesh
    Istio["Istio Service Mesh"] -.->|mTLS + AuthzPolicy| Proxy
    Istio -.->|mTLS| Catalog

